    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you said it's a \"necessary adjustment\" but that sounds like a value judgment. isn't it also true that for some small businesses, especially in towns where everybody knows everybody, raising prices just drives the locals away? doesn't that risk the whole business failing?",
